b75dfec1-c48e-428d-9fbe-8d477b5821cc.title: <player>
b75dfec1-c48e-428d-9fbe-8d477b5821cc.text: Hello. What do you do here?

58a289c4-90ec-46a6-95b4-7849ec5d407b.title: Dusuri
58a289c4-90ec-46a6-95b4-7849ec5d407b.text:
I'm Dusuri. I specialise in unique minerals that can't be
found on Gielinor.

ee0b9bce-d6cb-4a5d-b9af-455c9affa384.title: <player>
ee0b9bce-d6cb-4a5d-b9af-455c9affa384.text:
Can't be found on Gielinor? Where do they come from
then?

8bf80294-d3a7-41dc-904a-405f06b97217.title: Dusuri
8bf80294-d3a7-41dc-904a-405f06b97217.text:
To be honest, we don't fully know. All we know is that
they can be found within shooting stars.

dc0f8a98-1b70-4fa9-907e-d20f9c13132d.title: Dusuri
dc0f8a98-1b70-4fa9-907e-d20f9c13132d.text:
That's right. They fall from the sky from time to time.
They can be mined for the unique minerals that I
specialise in.

44e9d754-ac5e-4cc6-9e9f-fb44aa101a1a.title: Dusuri
44e9d754-ac5e-4cc6-9e9f-fb44aa101a1a.text:
If you ever come across one, I'd be happy to trade
you for any stardust you find.

18536c34-17ff-40d3-bf4c-bd1118ad2cbf.title: <player>
18536c34-17ff-40d3-bf4c-bd1118ad2cbf.text: Oh yes. I've seen those before.

7bbdabe9-9949-4edd-b00c-fb768220a287.title: Dusuri
7bbdabe9-9949-4edd-b00c-fb768220a287.text:
Wonderful. If you ever get any stardust from them,
I'd be happy to trade you for it.

f59958d6-a0a5-4515-988d-d6f718d5e57c.title: <player>
f59958d6-a0a5-4515-988d-d6f718d5e57c.text: I have some here. Can we trade?

options.text: What can you tell me about shooting stars?

b1b28df1-ce5b-4faf-9afb-3bb684506a41.title: Dusuri
b1b28df1-ce5b-4faf-9afb-3bb684506a41.text:
I have packs of gems and soft clay if they take your
fancy. I also have some interesting star fragments that
seem to be able to recolour certain metals.

c01e70de-78ef-4504-885e-cf838cdb73c7.title: Dusuri
c01e70de-78ef-4504-885e-cf838cdb73c7.text:
Most notably, I have a unique ring that we found
embedded within a star once. It seems to have magical
properties that we don't fully understand. What we do
know is that it can improve your skill while mining.

options.text: What can you tell me about shooting stars?

8a8f25cf-f42c-49aa-95c2-4217df04a6d4.title: <player>
8a8f25cf-f42c-49aa-95c2-4217df04a6d4.text: What can you tell me about shooting stars?

9fab33b8-fb46-4406-b19d-395edc0d398f.title: Dusuri
9fab33b8-fb46-4406-b19d-395edc0d398f.text:
Not a lot really. All I know is that they fall from the
sky from time to time and that you can mine them.

53966bc5-4a3c-4547-9a34-8b387501d794.title: Dusuri
53966bc5-4a3c-4547-9a34-8b387501d794.text:
If you want to know more, there's an observatory near
Ardougne that you might want to visit. They've done
some research into them.
